    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're proud to list this exceptional vehicle in mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. This car presents as near-flawless in every respect. The exterior finish is stunning, with paint that retains its original deep luster, free of scratches, chips, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and consistent, chrome and trim pieces are pristine, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, the carpets are immaculate, and every surface, button, and control functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, and the vehicle runs with the smooth, confident performance you'd expect from a car treated with exceptional care throughout its life. Service history is complete, and all systems \u2014 mechanical, electrical, and safety \u2014 are in perfect working order. If you're looking for a used vehicle that truly feels new, this is a rare find. Serious buyers are encouraged to come see it in person \u2014 it will not disappoint.",
